00:08:07.812 --> 00:08:09.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I unsealed Morn's will.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:08:11.651 --> 00:08:12.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He left everything to you.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:13.851 --> 00:08:17.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me? He left everything to me?</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:17.770 --> 00:08:18.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:21.209 --> 00:08:22.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn...</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:24.407 --> 00:08:26.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>dear, sweet Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:27.846 --> 00:08:28.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:40.923 --> 00:08:44.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The poor fool actually believed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you cared about him.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:44.602 --> 00:08:45.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:45.482 --> 00:08:47.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was up for hours</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>last night thinking about him.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:47.761 --> 00:08:50.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Calculating his net worth, no doubt.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:52.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We spent a lot of time together, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:54.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were obviously a lot closer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than I ever realized.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:56.278 --> 00:08:57.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>His financial records.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:01.477 --> 00:09:02.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is this some kind of joke?</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:02.917 --> 00:09:03.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:04.116 --> 00:09:05.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to this, he was broke.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:05.636 --> 00:09:06.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sarcastically ) No.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:07.315 --> 00:09:08.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How can that be?</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:09.753 --> 00:09:10.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He paid his bar bill</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the end of every month.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:10.914 --> 00:09:12.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That kind of money</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>must have come from somewhere.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:13.433 --> 00:09:16.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, he did have his shipping business.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:16.272 --> 00:09:19.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe all his assets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are tied up in inventory.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:20.351 --> 00:09:22.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course. Inventory.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:09:25.829 --> 00:09:29.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll unload everything,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and use the profits to...</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:09:30.428 --> 00:09:33.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, what's that smell?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Your inheritance.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:09:33.348 --> 00:09:35.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Livanian beets. Very ripe.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:09:36.706 --> 00:09:38.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's in the rest of these?</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:09:38.386 --> 00:09:39.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>More beets.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:09:40.225 --> 00:09:43.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it? That's all he had?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:09:43.505 --> 00:09:44.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid so.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:09:44.384 --> 00:09:45.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:47.543 --> 00:09:52.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Except for the contents of his quarters.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe he spent all his money</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:52.262 --> 00:09:56.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-on furnishings and works of art.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Objets d'art.</i></c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:56.740 --> 00:09:57.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:58.860 --> 00:10:00.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Objets d'art.</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:01.699 --> 00:10:03.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll hold an auction.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>People will pay a premium</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:10:03.818 --> 00:10:05.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to own something that used to be Morn's.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:11.296 --> 00:10:13.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure these are the right quarters?</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:13.256 --> 00:10:14.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:14.975 --> 00:10:15.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Figures.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:10:17.774 --> 00:10:18.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:10:19.493 --> 00:10:21.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That, I believe, is a matador.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:22.930 --> 00:10:24.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. That.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:10:25.132 --> 00:10:26.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: That's Morn's bed.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:10:27.291 --> 00:10:28.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn slept in...</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:10:29.251 --> 00:10:30.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>-mud? -Hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:10:31.330 --> 00:10:33.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm told it's excellent for the skin.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:10:37.728 --> 00:10:38.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks, Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:39.248 --> 00:10:40.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just what I always wanted.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:10:41.526 --> 00:10:42.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:10:45.805 --> 00:10:47.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing in my mud?</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:10:48.165 --> 00:10:53.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I... I couldn't resist.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Morny and I had so many happy times here,</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:10:53.837 --> 00:10:57.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just... I had to slip in.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry if I startled you.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:10:58.424 --> 00:11:00.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I heard you coming in</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I thought I'd better hide.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:01.201 --> 00:11:02.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are you?</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:02.807 --> 00:11:03.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um...</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:03.880 --> 00:11:04.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Larell.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:11:05.639 --> 00:11:07.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn's wife. Well, ex-wife.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:11:08.279 --> 00:11:09.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn was married?</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:11:09.999 --> 00:11:10.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To you?</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:11:11.117 --> 00:11:12.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For two wonderful years.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:11:13.557 --> 00:11:15.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must be Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:11:15.877 --> 00:11:18.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morny and I kept in touch</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after we were separated.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:11:19.275 --> 00:11:22.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He talked about you all the time.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:11:23.954 --> 00:11:24.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's nice.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:11:25.553 --> 00:11:28.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He told me that if anything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ever happened to him,</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:11:28.433 --> 00:11:31.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he wanted you to have everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that was ever his.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:11:32.872 --> 00:11:33.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything?</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:11:35.710 --> 00:11:36.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:11:39.669 --> 00:11:41.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm glad you came by,</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:11:42.189 --> 00:11:45.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because Morny didn't leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>me much of anything else.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:11:46.188 --> 00:11:47.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why, I find that hard to believe.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:11:47.907 --> 00:11:48.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:49.386 --> 00:11:51.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm as disappointed as you are.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:11:52.385 --> 00:11:53.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I happen to know</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:53.585 --> 00:11:57.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he had quite</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a substantial retirement fund,</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:57.304 --> 00:11:59.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>one that could make two people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>very comfortable.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:12:01.943 --> 00:12:05.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you're partial to mud,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's comfortable, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:12:06.541 --> 00:12:09.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm talking about the thousand bricks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of gold-pressed latinum</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:12:09.501 --> 00:12:11.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he won in the Lissepian Lottery.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:12:11.820 --> 00:12:13.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A thousand bricks?</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:12:13.819 --> 00:12:18.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mm-hmm. Now that he's gone, it's all ours.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:12:29.854 --> 00:12:32.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( vacuum slurping )</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:12:44.650 --> 00:12:45.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:12:46.962 --> 00:12:48.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you think?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm looking for the latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:12:49.768 --> 00:12:51.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must know where he kept it.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:12:52.887 --> 00:12:55.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't even know it existed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until you told me.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:00.125 --> 00:13:02.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm sure it's somewhere</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the station.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:03.850 --> 00:13:04.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do we know he didn't spend it already?</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:05.284 --> 00:13:07.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you, it was for his retirement.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:08.830 --> 00:13:11.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Poor Morn.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He never got a chance to enjoy it.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:13:12.601 --> 00:13:13.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But that doesn't mean we can't.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:13:15.360 --> 00:13:16.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know what you're doing.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:13:18.360 --> 00:13:19.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What am I doing?</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:21.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just so we're clear...</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:13:22.399 --> 00:13:24.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the latinum's mine.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:13:25.477 --> 00:13:29.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He may have left everything to you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I was his wife.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:13:30.397 --> 00:13:33.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could contest the will,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and tie you up in court for years.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:13:34.635 --> 00:13:35.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:13:36.275 --> 00:13:38.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But there's no reason</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it has to come to that.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:13:39.114 --> 00:13:41.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After all, a thousand bricks is plenty</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for both of us.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:13:42.952 --> 00:13:44.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is a lot of money.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:46.951 --> 00:13:52.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And as soon as we find it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll take a nice long vacation together.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:13:53.349 --> 00:13:55.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn would have wanted it that way.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:13:55.788 --> 00:13:57.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, he would have.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:14:05.985 --> 00:14:09.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The latinum's not on the station.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I looked everywhere. Evade.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:14:10.104 --> 00:14:12.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I even had my brother scan for it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the internal sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:14:13.103 --> 00:14:14.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, at least you have the painting.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:14:14.543 --> 00:14:17.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, forget the painting.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want that latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:14:17.742 --> 00:14:19.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you think it'll make you happy.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:14:19.182 --> 00:14:19.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Confront.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:14:20.541 --> 00:14:21.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Believe me, it will.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:14:24.604 --> 00:14:26.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the break I've been waiting for,</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:14:26.580 --> 00:14:28.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it's been a long time in coming.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:14:28.899 --> 00:14:31.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want Morn's money. I need Morn's money.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:14:32.898 --> 00:14:33.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I deserve Morn's money.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:14:35.816 --> 00:14:36.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your move.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:14:39.216 --> 00:14:43.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Beautiful, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And the way it picks up the light.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:14:44.574 --> 00:14:47.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wonder who came up with the idea</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of suspending liquid latinum</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:14:47.813 --> 00:14:49.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>inside worthless bits of gold?</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:14:49.893 --> 00:14:52.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Probably someone who got</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tired of making change</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:14:52.131 --> 00:14:53.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with an eyedropper.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:14:53.651 --> 00:14:54.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you going to play or not?</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:14:59.501 --> 00:15:00.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where do you think Morn put it all?</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:15:02.893 --> 00:15:03.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you find it, are you really</c.bg_transparent>
