231
00:15:04.608 --> 00:15:06.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I agreed to pay her ten percent</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so she wouldn't tie me up in court.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:15:06.847 --> 00:15:07.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's 100 bricks.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:15:08.527 --> 00:15:09.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What could I do?</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:15:09.647 --> 00:15:10.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Retreat.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:15:12.725 --> 00:15:15.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know, but there's something</c.bg_transparent>
