236
00:15:16.284 --> 00:15:17.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't trust this woman.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:15:20.683 --> 00:15:24.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Neither do I, but... that doesn't mean</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:15:24.162 --> 00:15:25.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to keep her away from my lobes.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:15:25.761 --> 00:15:28.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just keep your eyes open.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be fooled by a pretty face.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:15:28.961 --> 00:15:30.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not me.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:15:30.641 --> 00:15:32.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course not. Acquire.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:15:47.915 --> 00:15:48.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:15:50.674 --> 00:15:53.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What a pleasant surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:15:57.952 --> 00:15:59.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, lights.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:16:01.551 --> 00:16:04.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me... you like surprises, Quark?</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:16:05.310 --> 00:16:06.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only pleasant ones.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:16:07.509 --> 00:16:09.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I like to think I'm pleasant.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:16:09.429 --> 00:16:12.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You think I'm pleasant?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Absolutely.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:16:12.668 --> 00:16:16.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I guess this qualifies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as a pleasant surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:16:17.306 --> 00:16:18.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing in my quarters?</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:16:18.665 --> 00:16:19.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Waiting for you.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:16:19.905 --> 00:16:25.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My brother and I were business</c.bg_transparent>
