254
00:16:29.263 --> 00:16:30.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really? Was it nice?</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:16:30.582 --> 00:16:32.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was lovely.</c.bg_transparent>

256
