<c.bg_transparent>I understand you inherited Morn's estate.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:16:36.740 --> 00:16:37.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:16:38.539 --> 00:16:41.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're business associates of Morn's.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:16:41.619 --> 00:16:42.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your brother mentioned that.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:16:42.899 --> 00:16:46.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He... borrowed some money from us,</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:16:46.777 --> 00:16:51.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and we'd like the estate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to repay the loan.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:16:52.957 --> 00:16:53.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh-huh.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:16:53.856 --> 00:16:55.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How much money are we talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:16:56.214 --> 00:16:57.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:16:58.614 --> 00:17:02.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One thousand bricks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of gold-pressed latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:17:02.893 --> 00:17:05.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had a feeling</c.bg_transparent>
