268
00:17:12.610 --> 00:17:14.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We shook hands.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:17:15.895 --> 00:17:16.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We trusted Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:17:17.885 --> 00:17:22.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I'm sure he'd want you...</c.bg_transparent>
