277
00:17:49.639 --> 00:17:52.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not the first creditors</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to make a claim against his estate.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:17:53.117 --> 00:17:53.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're not?</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:17:54.837 --> 00:17:58.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
