<c.bg_transparent>What can we expect?</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:18:11.952 --> 00:18:12.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A percentage.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:18:13.151 --> 00:18:13.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What sort of percentage?</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:18:14.111 --> 00:18:14.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
