<c.bg_transparent>We can't accept less than 80.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:18:16.391 --> 00:18:17.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll make it 30,</c.bg_transparent>

289
