290
00:18:19.950 --> 00:18:20.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't like beets.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:18:21.309 --> 00:18:22.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll take 70.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:18:22.188 --> 00:18:22.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forty.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:18:23.690 --> 00:18:25.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And because I can see</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you both have fine taste,</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:18:26.228 --> 00:18:27.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm willing to part with this.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:18:28.277 --> 00:18:30.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of Morn's most treasured possessions.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:18:30.906 --> 00:18:32.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Beautiful, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:18:32.625 --> 00:18:34.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very nice.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:18:34.745 --> 00:18:35.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can't take less than 60.</c.bg_transparent>

299
