<c.bg_transparent>-Fifty.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:18:42.342 --> 00:18:43.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fifty it is.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:18:43.862 --> 00:18:47.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm glad we could come</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to an understanding.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:18:48.421 --> 00:18:49.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me, too.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:18:49.661 --> 00:18:50.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:18:53.420 --> 00:18:56.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be watching you, Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:18:57.990 --> 00:18:58.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't try anything.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:18:58.937 --> 00:19:00.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me? Don't be ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:19:16.253 --> 00:19:17.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do we have here?</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:19:22.891 --> 00:19:25.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, what is this?</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:26.769 --> 00:19:29.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>A claim slip</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>for Storage Locker 137,</i></c.bg_transparent>

311
00:19:29.609 --> 00:19:31.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>located in the Station Assay Office.</i></c.bg_transparent>

312
00:19:32.128 --> 00:19:33.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A storage locker!</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:19:34.807 --> 00:19:37.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, computer.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You've been very helpful.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:19:41.285 --> 00:19:44.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn, wherever you are, I love you!</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:19:47.403 --> 00:19:49.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have to open it in here?</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:19:49.842 --> 00:19:53.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Regulations, the contents</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of a deceased person's storage locker</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:19:53.162 --> 00:19:55.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>have to be inspected by station security.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:19:55.721 --> 00:19:58.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no such regulation.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You just want to know what's inside.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:19:58.279 --> 00:20:01.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are so transparent.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can't wait to see your face</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:20:01.119 --> 00:20:05.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when your deputies wheel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in my thousand bricks of latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:20:06.917 --> 00:20:09.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, here we are. Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:20:09.796 --> 00:20:10.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That can't be it.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:20:11.796 --> 00:20:14.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Storage Locker 137.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:20:17.434 --> 00:20:20.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well... sometimes,</c.bg_transparent>
