<c.bg_transparent>While the entire world was celebrating,</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:31:54.585 --> 00:31:56.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>someone broke into the Central Bank</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and made off with...</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:31:57.864 --> 00:32:00.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One thousand bricks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of gold-pressed latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:32:04.662 --> 00:32:05.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:32:06.182 --> 00:32:09.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You expect me to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the four of you pulled that off?</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:32:09.860 --> 00:32:11.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was five of us. Morn helped.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:32:12.140 --> 00:32:14.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, but then he ran off with the latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:32:15.539 --> 00:32:16.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why did you take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so long to come after him?</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:32:17.258 --> 00:32:19.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because we knew he'd stashed it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>away somewhere</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:32:19.578 --> 00:32:21.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to wait for the statute</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of limitations to expire.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:32:21.937 --> 00:32:23.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it did, two weeks ago.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:32:23.736 --> 00:32:25.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see, we can't be prosecuted anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:32:26.575 --> 00:32:27.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So here we are.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:32:27.895 --> 00:32:29.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The latinum's en route.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:32:30.454 --> 00:32:34.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we should just split it up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and go our separate ways.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:32:34.934 --> 00:32:35.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The voice of reason.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:32:36.213 --> 00:32:37.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not you...</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:32:39.972 --> 00:32:40.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>us.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:32:41.212 --> 00:32:42.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Krit's right. We don't need him anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:32:55.753 --> 00:32:56.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what do we do with him?</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:32:56.527 --> 00:32:58.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KRIT: It should look like an accident.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:32:58.286 --> 00:33:00.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't want anyone asking questions.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:33:01.860 --> 00:33:03.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait a minute. You can't kill me.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:33:03.965 --> 00:33:05.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the only one who can take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>delivery of the latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:33:06.244 --> 00:33:07.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need my thumb print.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:33:08.123 --> 00:33:10.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you stand still,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this won't hurt as much.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:33:10.482 --> 00:33:11.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screaming )</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:33:11.482 --> 00:33:12.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HAIN: Ah, ah, ah, wait a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:33:13.842 --> 00:33:15.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you propose, Nahsk?</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:33:15.601 --> 00:33:18.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That we walk into the Cargo Bay</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with his bloody thumb,</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:33:18.808 --> 00:33:19.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and ask for the latinum?</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:33:19.799 --> 00:33:20.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We need him.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:33:30.437 --> 00:33:34.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only question is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what happens after he takes delivery?</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:33:37.995 --> 00:33:41.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We could split the latinum... five ways.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:33:41.513 --> 00:33:44.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is what you would</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have gotten if Morn was still alive.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:33:44.192 --> 00:33:45.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's true.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:33:46.152 --> 00:33:47.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of me as Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:33:48.716 --> 00:33:49.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't believe I just said that.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:33:49.791 --> 00:33:51.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't fair. We stole it.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:33:51.711 --> 00:33:52.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He had nothing to do with it.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:33:52.910 --> 00:33:54.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe not, but the bottom line</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is you need me.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:33:56.709 --> 00:33:59.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A thousand bricks of latinum</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>split five ways...</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:34:02.867 --> 00:34:03.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>what do you think?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:34:05.506 --> 00:34:06.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's still a lot of latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:34:07.785 --> 00:34:11.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's 250 bricks each.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:34:12.944 --> 00:34:13.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So do we have a deal?</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:34:18.583 --> 00:34:20.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-All right.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-OK.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:34:20.541 --> 00:34:23.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Bolian transport</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>arrives tomorrow at 1600.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:34:24.220 --> 00:34:25.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll meet at the cargo bay.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:34:25.420 --> 00:34:26.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're staying together until it gets here.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:34:27.996 --> 00:34:27.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are?</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:34:28.200 --> 00:34:30.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't trust you, and I certainly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>don't trust them.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:34:30.899 --> 00:34:31.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see your point.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:34:32.418 --> 00:34:35.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I have a bar to run.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:34:38.776 --> 00:34:39.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:34:44.814 --> 00:34:45.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To your hospitality.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:34:46.254 --> 00:34:47.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't mention it.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:34:51.732 --> 00:34:53.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So this was Morn's favorite place?</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:34:54.118 --> 00:34:55.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He used to sit right there.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:34:55.771 --> 00:35:00.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, that's not very smart</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sitting with your back to the door.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:35:00.530 --> 00:35:02.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was the trusting type.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:35:03.649 --> 00:35:04.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which one of you killed him anyway?</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:35:06.648 --> 00:35:07.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't us.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:35:10.872 --> 00:35:11.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me neither.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:35:12.726 --> 00:35:13.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't look at me.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:35:14.766 --> 00:35:16.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then it really was an accident.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:35:18.124 --> 00:35:21.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Poor Morny. He always had such bad luck.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:35:27.362 --> 00:35:28.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get rid of him.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:35:31.760 --> 00:35:32.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're closed.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:35:33.680 --> 00:35:34.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At this hour?</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:35:37.279 --> 00:35:38.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Friends of Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:35:38.478 --> 00:35:40.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're... commiserating.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:35:40.917 --> 00:35:42.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:35:44.316 --> 00:35:46.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And how long are you going to be closed?</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:35:46.876 --> 00:35:50.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, until about 1600 hours tomorrow.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:35:52.594 --> 00:35:54.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have a lot to commiserate about.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:35:54.993 --> 00:35:56.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:36:04.708 --> 00:36:05.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where were we?</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:36:13.588 --> 00:36:14.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There it is.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:36:15.187 --> 00:36:16.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right on time.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:36:18.346 --> 00:36:19.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh...</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:36:19.546 --> 00:36:21.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe that's for me.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:36:37.540 --> 00:36:38.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open it.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:36:50.297 --> 00:36:51.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:36:52.536 --> 00:36:54.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll count it.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:36:54.775 --> 00:36:55.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:37:05.612 --> 00:37:06.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:37:07.172 --> 00:37:09.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somebody else count it.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:37:09.131 --> 00:37:14.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put it down, Hain. My brother may be slow,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but if you pull that trigger,</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:37:15.209 --> 00:37:16.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>he'll kill you.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:37:17.848 --> 00:37:19.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not slow.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:37:25.286 --> 00:37:26.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nahsk...</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:37:27.405 --> 00:37:29.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>what are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:37:30.525 --> 00:37:31.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're family.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:37:31.485 --> 00:37:34.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just put the gun down.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:37:44.600 --> 00:37:46.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( weapons fire continues )</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:37:48.319 --> 00:37:49.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:37:50.158 --> 00:37:51.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kill each other.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:37:53.118 --> 00:37:53.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:37:57.156 --> 00:37:59.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:37:59.276 --> 00:38:01.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: Security. Drop your weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:38:01.515 --> 00:38:03.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Huh?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( weapons fire continues )</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:38:03.874 --> 00:38:06.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: This is your last warning.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I said drop them.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:38:06.674 --> 00:38:07.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( weapon clatters to ground )</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:38:07.593 --> 00:38:08.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>LARELL: I surrender.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:38:10.633 --> 00:38:12.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take her to a holding cell.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:38:12.512 --> 00:38:14.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get the rest of them to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:38:21.669 --> 00:38:24.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, there you are.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:38:24.109 --> 00:38:25.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are they gone?</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:38:25.788 --> 00:38:28.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>From now on,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll be commiserating alone.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:38:28.987 --> 00:38:31.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All your "friends" are going to prison.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:38:32.669 --> 00:38:33.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For how long?</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:38:33.706 --> 00:38:35.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Assault with intent to kill?</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:38:35.905 --> 00:38:36.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Long enough.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:38:37.665 --> 00:38:39.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then it's mine.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:38:39.584 --> 00:38:41.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All mine.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:38:42.983 --> 00:38:44.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What you are about to hear</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:38:45.342 --> 00:38:48.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is the most beautiful sound in the galaxy.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:38:53.980 --> 00:38:55.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that can't be.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:38:55.979 --> 00:38:57.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no latinum in these bricks.</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:38:57.979 --> 00:38:58.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:38:59.418 --> 00:39:02.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Someone's extracted all the latinum!</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:39:03.174 --> 00:39:05.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing here but worthless gold.</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:39:05.376 --> 00:39:07.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it's all yours.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:39:07.615 --> 00:39:09.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:39:10.153 --> 00:39:11.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:39:12.134 --> 00:39:15.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No! No!</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:39:30.609 --> 00:39:31.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:39:32.484 --> 00:39:34.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quark? Quark?</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:39:34.448 --> 00:39:35.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:39:36.167 --> 00:39:37.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want?</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:39:37.727 --> 00:39:39.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's someone here to see you.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:39:39.526 --> 00:39:42.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought you said</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they were all going to prison.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:39:42.285 --> 00:39:43.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'd better sit down.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:39:47.324 --> 00:39:48.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn?</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:39:48.603 --> 00:39:49.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alive and well.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:39:50.842 --> 00:39:52.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apparently, he faked his own death,</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:39:53.423 --> 00:39:55.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'll let him tell you all about it.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:40:02.319 --> 00:40:03.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well?</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:40:03.678 --> 00:40:04.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:40:04.958 --> 00:40:06.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:40:06.717 --> 00:40:08.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not one word.</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:40:08.717 --> 00:40:09.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You set me up.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:40:13.676 --> 00:40:15.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You left the latinum to me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because you knew I would do</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:40:16.754 --> 00:40:18.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>whatever it would take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get my hands on it.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:40:18.554 --> 00:40:20.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You figured I could keep the four of them</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:40:20.194 --> 00:40:22.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>off-balance long enough for them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to turn on themselves.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:40:22.793 --> 00:40:26.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This whole thing was a scam</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get them off your back, wasn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:40:30.951 --> 00:40:32.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could have been killed, you know.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:40:39.748 --> 00:40:42.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I thought we were friends.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:40:47.266 --> 00:40:48.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to admit...</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:40:48.906 --> 00:40:51.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't suspect for a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:40:51.625 --> 00:40:52.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell you the truth,</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:40:52.784 --> 00:40:55.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't think you had it in you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to pull off something like this.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:40:55.783 --> 00:40:57.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just have one question for you.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:40:57.343 --> 00:40:58.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to the latinum?</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:41:10.139 --> 00:41:13.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gurgling burp )</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:41:18.456 --> 00:41:21.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course. Your second stomach.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:41:24.548 --> 00:41:26.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been keeping it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in your second stomach</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:41:26.374 --> 00:41:27.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all these years?</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:41:29.893 --> 00:41:31.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a lot of latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:41:31.292 --> 00:41:32.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No wonder your hair fell out.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:41:39.450 --> 00:41:40.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For me?</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:41:44.969 --> 00:41:50.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That must be 100 bricks worth.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what to say.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:41:51.527 --> 00:41:52.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks.</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:41:52.526 --> 00:41:54.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not that I didn't earn it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after all you put me through.</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:41:57.565 --> 00:42:00.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you ever want to set</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>me up again, feel free.</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:42:03.883 --> 00:42:04.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know...</c.bg_transparent>

715
00:42:06.562 --> 00:42:09.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you and I should consider</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doing business together.</c.bg_transparent>

716
00:42:09.721 --> 00:42:12.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two enterprising gentlemen like us</c.bg_transparent>

717
00:42:12.360 --> 00:42:17.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>could do all right for ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Take that gold dust of yours...</c.bg_transparent>

718
00:42:18.839 --> 00:42:20.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it doesn't have to be a total loss.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:42:20.917 --> 00:42:22.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hear there's some primitive cultures</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:42:23.776 --> 00:42:24.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who consider it quite valuable.</c.bg_transparent>

